HEADWORD: Recharge
<hw>Re*charge"</hw> <pr>(r⟦emac⟧*ch⟦aum⟧rj")</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos>
<ety>[Pref. <ets>re-</ets> + <ets>charge</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>recharger</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To charge or accuse in
